data.description: Newly renovated, updated fourplex in North Las Vegas! Recent renovations include new AC unit, new fencing, new irrigation system, new kitchen cabinets, new flooring, new plumbing etc. There is an assumable FHA loan on this one at 3.75%. Only owner occupant can assume. 2 units have traditional tenants. 2 units are furnished and have great AIRBNB potential. Furnishings in units 3 and 4 can be included with the sale. This property has serious cash flow potential. All units are the same layout. 1 parking spot per unit in driveway. Additional parking is possible on the street. NO HOA. Starting Jan. 1st, 3 units will be available. Clean slate to place new tenants at current market rates. Conveniently located to freeways, parks, library, shopping, restaurants and more!
